 ERM. Finally, numerical examples\nare displayed in order to provide strong empirical evidence that the approach\nwe promote largely surpasses more naive subsampling techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jan 2015 12:58:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2015 22:42:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 12:42:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 06:30:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-25"}
