rent practical open quantum systems in atomic, quantum\noptical, and cold matter systems, which are treated qualitatively by a\nfew-level master equation model before.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jan 2015 14:28:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-22"}
